class Attribute:
    TYPE_NOMINAL = 1
    TYPE_NUMERICAL = 2
    
    def __init__(self, name: str, domain: set, type_of_att=TYPE_NOMINAL):  
        this.name = name
        this.domain  = domain
        this.type = type_of_att
